  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Agent Audiobook Maker的MVP阶段画一个系统上下文图。核心是这个工具跑在本地机器上，操作者通过命令行来驱动整个流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator",
        "cli",
        "abm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以Operator是一个Person角色，他直接跟CLI交互。这个CLI具体承担什么职责？是单纯的入口还是也有编排能力？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator",
        "cli"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CLI同时是编排器（Orchestrator），它负责运行整个pipeline，管理多个agents的执行，而且支持断点续传——就是deterministic resume。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cli",
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以CLI/Orchestrator是一个System，内部会调用Agents Suite。那这些agents具体有哪些？我需要列出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cli",
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Agents Suite作为一个整体系统就行，内部包含Dialogue、Speaker、Alias、Casting、SSML、TTS、Mastering这些模块。MVP阶段先不展开每个agent的细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解。那数据存储怎么处理？我看到有提到Postgres和文件系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pg",
        "fs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要两个存储。Postgres用JSONB存结构化数据：books、chapters、annotations、characters、tts_profiles、stems、renders这些表。Filesystem存实际文件，按data/目录组织，分clean、annotations、ssml、stems、renders几个子目录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pg",
        "fs",
        "cli"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，Postgres是SystemDb类型，Filesystem是System类型。CLI对两者都是读写关系。那整个本地环境需要包在一个边界里吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "abm",
        "cli",
        "pg",
        "fs",
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，用System Boundary把本地机器上的所有组件包起来，命名为\"Agent Audiobook Maker (Local Machine)\"。Operator在边界外，因为他虽然是本地运行，但代表的是人的角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "abm",
        "operator",
        "cli",
        "pg",
        "fs",
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下：Operator调用CLI，CLI分别读写Postgres和Filesystem，同时调用Agents Suite。所有内部组件放在ABM边界内。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator",
        "cli",
        "pg",
        "fs",
        "agents",
        "abm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Operator和CLI的关系描述要准确一点，不只是\"调用\"，还包括监控执行过程，所以应该是\"Invokes, monitors\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator",
        "cli"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正关系描述为\"Invokes, monitors\"。另外CLI和Agents的关系是\"Invokes\"，和Postgres、Filesystem都是\"Reads/Writes\"，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator",
        "cli",
        "pg",
        "fs",
        "agents"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。还有布局配置，MVP阶段组件不多，希望形状排成3列，边界只占1行高度，这样比较紧凑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "$c4ShapeInRow",
        "$c4BoundaryInRow"
