      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加UpdateLayoutConfig，设置$c4ShapeInRow=\"3\"，$c4BoundaryInRow=\"1\"。现在内部四个系统（CLI、Postgres、Filesystem、Agents）会排成一行三列的效果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "$c4ShapeInRow",
        "$c4BoundaryInRow",
        "cli",
