        "$c4ShapeInRow"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，保持$c4ShapeInRow=\"3\"。这样第一行可能是CLI、Postgres、Filesystem，Agents在第二行居中，或者根据C4的自动布局调整。标题定为\"Agent Audiobook Maker – System Context (MVP)\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
