    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。再确认一下Postgres的描述，要突出JSONB的使用场景，这是技术选型的一个关键点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Postgres的描述已定为：\"JSONB: books, chapters, annotations, characters, tts_profiles, stems, renders\"。这样直接体现了schema-less的设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pg"
