      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Operator的描述也需要准确：\"Runs CLI locally; reviews outputs\"，强调本地执行和人工审核两个职责。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "operator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已更新。Filesystem的描述是\"data/: clean, annotations, ssml, stems, renders\"，这样目录结构也清晰了。",
