    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。CLI作为中心枢纽：Operator invokes CLI，CLI reads/writes Postgres，CLI reads/writes Filesystem，CLI invokes Agents。没有绕开CLI的直接连接，符合MVP的集中式设计。图已完成。",
